"\n"
"    In maintenance mode the application responds with HTTP 503 and a "
"maintenance page.\n"
"    Whitelisted paths (health endpoint, static files) and any configured ops "
"IPs\n"
"    remain reachable. The toggle takes effect immediately once the flag file "
"is written.\n"
"    "

